OL,3,CCraig Bellamy 'grateful' to be
OL,4,Cappointed as new Wales manager
OL,6,FCraig Bellamy has said he is
OL,7,F"grateful" for the opportunity to be
OL,8,Fthe new Wales manager.
OL,10,FBellamy succeeds Rob Page, who was
OL,11,Fsacked last month in the wake of
OL,12,Ffailing to qualify for Euro 2024.
OL,14,FThe 44-year-old is a former Wales
OL,15,Fcaptain, who won 78 caps for his
OL,16,Fcountry between 1998 and 2013.
