OL,3,CCraig Bellamy 'grateful' to be
OL,4,Cappointed as new Wales manager
OL,6,FSpeaking at a press conference on
OL,7,FWednesday for the first time since
OL,8,Fbeing appointed, Bellamy said: "The
OL,9,Flast three, four months it sort of
OL,10,Fbecame clear to me that I was happy
OL,11,Fbut I needed more.
OL,13,F"It became clear to me that I needed
OL,14,Fto look for a number one spot for me,
OL,15,Fas a person for my progression and
OL,16,Fobviously didn't know what that was
OL,17,Fgoing to be at that time.
