OL,3,CCraig Bellamy 'grateful' to be
OL,4,Cappointed as new Wales manager
OL,6,F"And then I just sort of made it clear
OL,7,Fto myself that this is what it's going
OL,8,Fto be, this is how I'm going to go
OL,9,Fabout it and then obviously the
OL,10,Fsituation changed here with Wales."
OL,12,FThe former Wales player began his
OL,13,Fcoaching career in the academy of
OL,14,Fhometown club Cardiff.
